{
  "chapter": 278,
  "chapter_summary": "第二百七十八章讲述项少龙与曹秋道在桓公台上的十招之约决斗。项少龙事先布置逃命索，以刀鞘宝石反射火光干扰曹秋道视线的策略争取先机，随后发动消耗战，连续抢攻使曹秋道难以掌控节奏。十招过后曹秋道食言继续追杀，项少龙失去刀鞘陷入绝境，却以跃空双手劈斩的拼命招式削断曹秋道斩将剑两寸剑锋。最终项少龙力竭退至石栏边，以翻身坠台的方式逃脱，借事先准备的腰索逃命。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "上次拜领上将军绝艺，曹某回味无穷，今晚务请上将军不吝赐教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "本人乃曹公剑下败军之将，何足言勇，请曹公手下留情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "败的是曹某才对，当晚上将军用的不是趁手兵器，曹某能挫上将军，只是侥幸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "曹某剑出鞘后，从不留手，只有以生死相搏，才能表达剑手对剑的敬意。上将军这把刀有名字吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "刀名'百战'，请曹公赐教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "十多年来，除了一个人外，再无其他人能在曹某面前站得如此稳当。对手难求，上将军可知曹某的欣悦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这把剑乃曹某亲自冶炼，剑名'斩将'，上将军小心了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "曹公请先出手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "总有一人须先出手的，看剑！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好刀！曹某从未试过如此痛快。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "项某实非前辈对手，现在十招之数已足，大家可止息干戈了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "笑话！什么十招之数？上将军乃我东方诸国头号大敌，你以为我曹秋道会让你活着回去吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "失去刀鞘，看你还能玩得出什么花样？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "曹公请三思，刚才若项某要求个两败俱伤，非是不可能的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以曹某之命，换上将军之命，也是非常划算。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "这该由我来决定，而非由曹公决定。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你以为可激怒曹某吗？倒要看看你还有什么本领。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "speaker_name": "曹秋道",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还有什么话好说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_cao_qiu_dao",
      "text": "多谢曹公赐教，小弟要走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 278,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    }
  ],
